  "dua1Arabic": "رَبَّنَا آتِنَا فِي الدُّنْيَا حَسَنَةً وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ حَسَنَةً وَقِنَا عَذَابَ النَّارِ",
  "dua1Transliteration": "Rabbana atina fid-dunya hasanatan wa fil-akhirati hasanatan wa qina azaban-nar",
  "dua1Meaning": "Our Lord, give us good in this world and good in the Hereafter, and protect us from the punishment of the Fire.",
  "dua2Arabic": "اللَّهُمَّ بَارِكْ لَنَا فِي رِزْقِنَا",
  "dua2Transliteration": "Allahumma barik lana fi rizqina",
  "dua2Meaning": "O Allah, bless us in our provision.",
  "dua3Arabic": "اللَّهُمَّ اغْفِرْ لِي وَارْحَمْنِي",
  "dua3Transliteration": "Allahumma ighfir li warhamni",
  "dua3Meaning": "O Allah, forgive me and have mercy on me.",
  "dua4Arabic": "اللَّهُمَّ أَعِنِّي عَلَى ذِكْرِكَ وَشُكْرِكَ وَحُسْنِ عِبَادَتِكَ",
  "dua4Transliteration": "Allahumma a'inni ala dhikrika wa shukrika wa husni ibadatika",
  "dua4Meaning": "O Allah, help me to remember You, to thank You, and to worship You in the best way.",
  "dua5Arabic": "رَبِّ اجْعَلْنِي مُقِيمَ الصَّلَاةِ وَمِنْ ذُرِّيَّتِي",
  "dua5Transliteration": "Rabbi ij'alni muqimas-salati wa min dhurriyyati",
  "dua5Meaning": "My Lord, make me and my descendants establish prayer.",
